<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE> Schizophrenia Treatment:  Questions To Ask Your Doctor For Choosing 
The Right Medication
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<body    bgcolor="#ffffff"  text="#000000"  link="#0000ee" vlink="551a8b" alink="ff0000">

<center>

<H6><I>

