<TITLE>NAMI Reports Deep Flaws, Money Wasted in System
Designed to Help Persons With Severe Mental Illnesses Get Jobs
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<body    bgcolor="#ffffff"  text="#000000"  link="#0000ee" vlink="551a8b" alink="ff0000">

<center>

<H6><I>

<A HREF = "/index.html" target="_top">NAMI</A> /

