<p><b>Obsessive-Compulsive Disorder (OCD)</b></p>

<ol>
    <li>&nbsp;California Alliance for the Mentally Ill, <i>The
        Journal of the CA Alliance for the Mentally Ill</i>, Volume
        6, Number 1, 1995.</li>
    <li>&nbsp;MA Jenike, <i>Drug Treatment of OCD in Adults</i>,
        May 1996.</li>
    <li>&nbsp;National Institute of Mental Health, <i>Obsessive-Compulsive
        Disorder</i> (pamphlet), September 1994.</li>
    <li>&nbsp;Obsessive Compulsive Information Center, Dean
        Foundation for Health, <i>Obsessive Compulsive Disorder:
        A Guide</i>, 1995.</li>
</ol>

<p><b>Major Depression and Bipolar Disorder</b></p>

<ol>
    <li>National Alliance for the Mentally Ill, <i>Understanding
        Major Depression</i>: <i>What You Need to Know About this
        Medical Illness</i> (brochure), 1995.</li>
