<td colspan=5>



<a name="8"><H3>FASHION, SPORTING GOODS<br>& CONSUMABLE PRODUCTS<hr></H3></a>



<P>Includes advertisements for clothing, clothing accesories, jewelry, watches, furs, 
golf, tennis and aerobic equipment, leather goods (including luggage) and 
consumable products such as chocolate and liquors.</P>



<STRONG>Non-Contract Rates<hr></STRONG>
