<br><br>

<P>Halftones -- 85 line screen. Highlight dot should not be less than .006 inches in 
diameter (15%), and shadow dots should not be less than .007 inches in 
diameter (80%). The placement of the 50% dot should be between 0.60-0.70 
density units away from the placement of the highlight dot.</P>




<P>	For special-effect screens, the above requirements should be used as a guide. 
Fine lines and serifs should not be less than .006 inches in thickness.</P>



<STRONG>Deadline And Mailing Instructions</STRONG><br><br>


