Deals make Wall Street hum, and in this special report, we'll review the hottest deals of the year...and track how they look at year's end. How well were investors rewarded, how bright is the future for these new ventures? Must-reading for Wall Street professionals, bankers, brokers and investors of all stripes.
<blockquote>
<img src="../IMAGES/pixel.gif"> December 15<BR>
