<H3><HR NOSHADE>
Canadian Scientists dine with <A HREF="scientists/Galdikas/galdikas.html">Orangutans</A>.<BR>
Canadian Scientists fight the <A HREF="scientists/Kimura/kimura.html">battle of the sexes</A>.<BR>
