is SHOCKED! Try the <A HREF="scientists/Ricker/ricker.html#game">Salmon Game</A> if you have the <A HREF="http://www.macromedia.com/Tools/Shockwave/index.html">ShockWave</A> plug-in for Netscape 2.0. <BR>

