<DOCNO>WT02-B26-256</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA097-001047-B045-133</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.science.ca:80/scientists/Galdikas/galdikas.html 142.58.111.137 19970215091639 text/html 13056
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 15 Feb 1997 09:16:54 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Fri, 29 Nov 1996 21:32:12 GMT
