</TD>

<TR>

<TD VALIGN=TOP><IMG SRC="../../graphics/bullet.gif"></TD>

<TD VALIGN=TOP><B>Family Members</B></TD>

<TD>



Father: Israel Brockhouse<BR>

Mother: Mabel Emily Neville<BR>

Spouse: Doris Miller, worked as film cutter at NFB<BR>

Children: Anne, Gordon, Ian, James, Beth, and Charles. Also 8 grandchildren.

</TD>

</TR>
<TR>

<TD VALIGN=TOP><IMG SRC="../../graphics/bullet.gif"></TD>

<TD><B>Title</B></TD><TD>  Professor Emeritus, McMaster University </TD>

</TR>

<TR>

<TD VALIGN=TOP><IMG SRC="../../graphics/bullet.gif"></TD>

<TD><B>Status</B></TD>

<TD>Retired and studying the philosophy of science</TD>

</TR>
<TR>

<TD VALIGN=TOP><IMG SRC="../../graphics/bullet.gif"></TD>

<TD VALIGN=TOP><B>Degrees</B></TD>

<TD>

<UL>

