<FONT SIZE="+3"><B>Walter & Memory Lewis</B></FONT><BR>

<B><FONT SIZE="+2"> Ethnobotanists Walter Lewis and Memory
Elvin-Lewis

</FONT></B><BR>

</TD>

<TD>

<FONT COLOR="#FF0000" SIZE="+2"><I> World experts on airborne and

allergenic pollen. Famous for targeting medicinal plants in the

